snippet.title: Darksiders 4 - Official Announcement Trailer | THQ Nordic Digital Showcase 2025
snippet.description:
Watch the Announcement Trailer for Darksiders 4, the upcoming addition to the hit hack-and-slash RPG action franchise developed by Gunfire Games. Players will be brought back to the fight with the Four Horsemen in a rageful war fought in tandem with others and never alone. Darksiders 4 is coming soon to PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and PC.

#IGN #Darksiders4

snippet.title: The Conjuring: Last Rites | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover why this case ended it all. #TheConjuring: Last Rites - Only in Theaters September 5.

From New Line Cinema comes the ninth entry in the more than $2 billion theatrical Conjuring universe, The Conjuring: Last Rites, directed by franchise veteran Michael Chaves and produced by franchise architects James Wan and Peter Safran.

The Conjuring: Last Rites delivers another thrilling chapter of the iconic Conjuring cinematic universe, based on real events.  Vera Farmiga and Patrick Wilson reunite for one last case as renowned, real-life paranormal investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren in a powerful and spine-chilling addition to the global box office-breaking franchise.

Farmiga and Wilson star alongside Mia Tomlinson and Ben Hardy, who portray Ed and Lorraine‚Äôs daughter Judy Warren and her boyfriend, Tony Spera, as well as Steve Coulter returning as Father Gordon, Rebecca Calder, Elliot Cowan, K√≠la Lord Cassidy, Beau Gadsdon, John Brotherton and Shannon Kook.

Chaves directs from a screenplay by Ian Goldberg & Richard Naing and David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick, story by David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick & James Wan, based on characters created by Chad Hayes & Carey W. Hayes.  The executive producers are Michael Clear, Judson Scott, Hans Ritter, David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick, Natalia Safran, John Rickard and Michael Chaves.

Chaves is joined behind the camera by his creative team, including director of photography Eli Born, production designer John Frankish, editors Elliot Greenberg and Gregory Plotkin, visual effects supervisor Scott Edelstein, visual effects producer Eric Bruneau and costume designer Graham Churchyard, with casting by Rose Wicksteed and Sophie Kingston-Smith.  The music supervisor is Ian Broucek and the music is by composer Benjamin Wallfisch.

New Line Cinema Presents The Safran Company / An Atomic Monster Production, The Conjuring: Last Rites.  The film will be released worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and will be only in theaters and IMAX¬Æ in North America on September 5, 2025, and internationally beginning 3 September 2025.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

#Roblox #foltyn

id.title: MARVEL STUDIOS SPIDER-MAN TEASER HARI BARU 2026
id.description:
Teaser Hari Baru Marvel Studios Spider-Man 2026. Tampilan Pertama Kostum Spider-Man Baru, Tom Holland Spider-Man, Bruce Banner Hulk, Jon Bernthal Punisher, Teaser Mr Negative, Koneksi Avengers Doomsday & Adegan Pasca-Kredit Fantastic Four ‚ñ∫ https://bit.ly/AwesomeSubscribe

Tampilan Perdana Spider-Man Brand New Day https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lCmqSbnYfo0&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
Trailer Avengers: Kiamat https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bQfK5VSwLHQ&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
Video Baru yang Luar Biasa https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FeOfhzu7ZdY&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczxQXxyV_2D8kuEs_QsuQIyJ&index=7

Meliputi Teaser Spider-Man Brand New Day, Tampilan Pertama Kostum Spider-Man Baru. Pengumuman Hulk. Mengapa Bruce Banner akan membantu Spider-Man, Spider-Man vs Hulk, referensi sebelumnya tentang Hulk dalam film Spider-Man. Stan Lee, Incredible Hulk dan Spider-Man Live Action Crossover di tahun 1980-an.

Penjelasan Spider-Man Brand New Day. Penjahat Baru, Perubahan Tom Holland dalam Spider-Man, Koneksi Trailer Avengers Doomsday. Karakter Baru, Kostum Spider-Man Baru. Trailer Spider-Man Beyond The Spider-Verse dari Cinemacon. Trailer Spider-Man Noir, Koneksi Sadie Sink dengan Tobey Maguire dan Spider-Man.

Trailer Teaser Avengers Doomsday. Robert Downey Jr. Doctor Doom, The New Black Panther, Karakter X-Men, Doctor Strange, Avengers: Secret Wars, Tampilan Pertama Battleworld di MCU. Trailer Fantastic Four, Tampilan Pertama Franklin Richards. Ian McKellen Magneto, Patrick Stewart Professor X, Kesley Grammer Beast, Thor Returns, Mystique, Cyclops, Nightcrawler, Kembalinya X-Men Asli.

Easter Egg Deadpool dan Wolverine. Lelucon Deadpool vs Disney, Lelucon Kevin Feige Marvel dan Penghancuran Tembok Keempat. Lelucon Adegan Pasca Kredit Deadpool dan Wolverine. Mengapa Deadpool Menyelamatkan Wolverine, X-Men, Fantastic Four, dan Deadpool Menyelamatkan MCU. Bagaimana Deadpool dan Wolverine Mempersiapkan Avengers 6: Secret Wars dengan Battleworld dan Loki Musim 2 Berakhir dengan God Loki. Easter Egg Crossover

Mengapa Marvel me-reboot MCU, semua film Marvel dan Disney plus acara TV Marvel dengan Avengers 6: Secret Wars. Apa yang akan berubah dengan semua Avengers, Iron Man Baru, Mutan X-Men seperti Wolverine, Deadpool, Fantastic Four, Ghost Rider, Spider-Man, dan karakter lainnya?

Hugh Jackman Wolverine, MCU Wolverine. Teaser Avengers 6 Secret Wars, masa depan Wolverine, X-Men di MCU. Banyak lagi Trailer Marvel yang akan datang: Trailer Avengers Doomsday, Trailer Fantastic Four & banyak lagi!

Lebih banyak video Spider-Man Brand New Day segera hadir, video Avengers Doomsday, Fantastic Four & Superman!

snippet.title: Spider-Man: Alone | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Be the first to know when we launch! Follow our Indiegogo Pre-Launch Page: [https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/spider-man-alone-episode-1/coming_soon/]

Happy National Spider-Man Day! From Golden Century Films and our "Marvel Inspire" universe, this is the official teaser trailer for 'Spider-Man: Alone.'

'Spider-Man: Alone' is a deeply personal, character-driven fan series that plunges into the heart of Peter Parker's earliest days. A modern, street-level reimagining of Amazing Fantasy #15, our story explores the profound isolation and immense weight of newfound powers. This is the story of a boy learning to fly, and the agonizing, often lonely, process of what it cost him to become a hero.

This project is also proud to launch our Inspired Action initiative in partnership with the non-profit Friendly Neighborhood Activist, aiming to turn on-screen heroism into real-world change.

Follow the Journey & Join Our Community:
‚ñ∫ Instagram: [https://www.instagram.com/goldencenturyfilms/]
‚ñ∫ Twitter/X: [https://x.com/GoldenCenturyTV?t=nvrx03KCKC60Z4TcAYX5KA&s=09]
‚ñ∫ Facebook: [https://www.facebook.com/share/1GUwgCDW4o/]

About This Project:
'Spider-Man: Alone' is a non-profit fan film. This project is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to Marvel, Sony, or any of their subsidiaries. It is a passion project created by fans, for fans, in celebration of a character who has inspired us our entire lives. The pilot will be available for free.

snippet.description:

üé• Attention viewers! (ITS FAN MADE)
The web-slinger returns in Spider-Man: Brand New Day, the next chapter in the Marvel Cinematic Universe. Following the events of No Way Home, Peter Parker (Tom Holland) starts over with a new identity, a new life‚Ä¶ and new enemies. But with great power still comes great responsibility.
Watch the official Spider-Man: Brand New Day trailer‚Äîfeaturing Tom Holland, Zendaya, Sadie Sink, and a darker path for the hero we thought we knew.

The inspiration behind this video:
The web of destiny spins again in Spider-Man: Brand New Day, the highly anticipated return of Tom Holland‚Äôs Peter Parker. After the events of Spider-Man: No Way Home, Peter is left with no allies, no identity, and a dangerous new city to protect. But a new Spider-Man movie means new threats, new alliances, and a new home. This Spider-Man Brand New Day trailer introduces powerful new characters, including Sadie Sink, and teases the emotional evolution of Spider-Man as he embraces a darker path to redemption. Get ready for an action-packed Spider-Man 2026 trailer experience filled with stunning VFX, multiversal twists, and grounded storytelling in true Marvel fashion. Join the hype with visuals inspired by FilmSpot Trailer, TeaserPRO, MovieGasm, KinoCheck, and EmergencyAwesome.

From Marvel Studios and the creators of the MCU, this concept trailer blends the energy of Spider-Man: No Way Home with the bold possibilities of Spider-Man 4: Brand New Day. What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: This Roblox Scammer Promised to Quit, So I Stalked Him...
snippet.description:
...and it turns out I found him doing something even worse.

ElijahGives is infamously known as Roblox's most desperate scammer, and he told me he was going to quit. So after Elijah promised me to stop scamming kids on roblox, I secretly stalked him and figured out his previous scams and cybercrimes he committed in the past.

And while I thought he gave up scamming because he got relentlessly cyberbullied for being a pathetic scammer, it turns out Elijah's dark past caught up to him and caused even more problems.

snippet.title: Past Life #4 - Improv is a Blast!
snippet.description:
Past Life is an odd mix of a Social and PvP Minecraft game started by Grian. Players are thrown into a tiny world with almost no rules, except survive as long as possible.

In Past Life, we will be playing through the older versions of Minecraft and updating to a newer one each episode.

3+ Lives = Green Player
2 Lives = Yellow Player
1 Life = Red Player

Red Players are given the goal of killing all the other players in the game. Yellow Players can kill Green Players.

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. ‚ÄúAlpha‚Äù, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.
